{"tid":1738511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【希望在於黎明】史稱「11.18 小六四鎮壓」逾千名手足！打不倒香港人！","createTime":"2019-11-19T09:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T09:31:09.000Z","uid":167548,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"267760f1b7525372492a722ea8525d1e6f10b8b5","tid":1738511,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:18:52.000Z","msg":"今晚早啲休息, 聽日話比世界聽, 更重要話比200萬手足聽！<br />\n即使前者倒下了, 亦仍然有後者頂上！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">聽朝好關鍵！聽朝好關鍵！聽朝好關鍵！</span><br />\n決定流水抗爭嘅未來, 頂硬上聚多次氣勢返黎！頂到星期五股市收市！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DaOHY1K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDaOHY1K.png&h=8593b074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f5Qfzys.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff5Qfzys.jpg&h=bbfc92cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【行動方針】黎明行動 黃昏歸家<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eyzLCS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eyzLCS</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\nBE WATER<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共用緊慢性天安門式鎮壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\npopo式鳩拉鎮壓/暗殺將成主調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地是唔是要認清一個事實,<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">就是我方嘅抗爭武力靠實彈/車攻已可鎮壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n土共唔需要出老解去攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\nThomas Tang : 攬炒  我們都錯了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1738165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1738165</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n攬炒沒錯！但是我地沒能力逼佢地出老解！<br />\nor 運動鄧小強嘅鎮壓已足夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解決方法：<br />\n星期一至五 黎明出動 <span style=\"color: red;\">收市前回家！</span><br />\n夜晚損耗太多, 港豬訓曬覺, 嬲完就繼續返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期六日：善用制度拎不反！<br />\n若無則不強求, 當做休息日！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">不被捕 不陣地</span></span></strong><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n長期抗爭好簡單<br />\n繼續黎明行動 日落前回家！<br />\n星期一至五鬧長命<br />\n其實每次黎明行動搞死左早上交通,<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">拉得最多人嘅反而是中午下午<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n1</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a27b23be2df1b32b469fac1e4f8155adc6d44ffa","tid":1738511,"uid":287547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:19:21.000Z","msg":"[黃色經濟圈]你買我就代你捐一半<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1738473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1738473</a>"},{"pid":"5befe4488f5a63e57239062730eba611a8a76dbb","tid":1738511,"uid":269148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:20:05.000Z","msg":"最後通牒 12點前解除包圍理工大學<br />\n否則無差別裝修尖沙咀 火燒名店<br />\n<br />\n有無得諗"},{"pid":"39e4d35da6a87620604d09f5988ce490e6a7bc1c","tid":1738511,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:20:18.000Z","msg":"Thomas Tang : 攬炒  我們都錯了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1738165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1738165</a><br />\nPOST沒全文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/they-are-here-to-kill-what-would-could-you-do/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fthey-are-here-to-kill-what-would-could-you-do%2F&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqqooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=25cf9048\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fthey-are-here-to-kill-what-would-could-you-do%2F&h=c858